z-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Tong_quat_ve_lo_to_la_gi\" >T\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Cac_dieu_kien_khi_tham_gia_vao_lo_to_la_gi\" >C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n khi tham gia v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Tong_hop_thuat_ngu_quan_trong_khi_tham_gia_choi_lo_to\" >T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quan tr\u1ecdng khi tham gia ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4\u00a0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Lo_xien_So_da\" >L\u00f4 xi\u00ean\/ S\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Bao_lo_Danh_lo\" >Bao l\u00f4\/ \u0110\u00e1nh l\u00f4<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Bach_thu_lo\" >B\u1ea1ch th\u1ee7 l\u00f4<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Song_thu_lo\" >Song th\u1ee7 l\u00f4<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Huong_dan_cach_don_gian_de_choi_lo_to_la_gi\" >H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">SV368<\/a> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/lo-to-la-gi\/\">l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/a> c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3 v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1. \u0110\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00eau trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 th\u00fa v\u1ecb &amp; th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n nh\u00e9!<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tong_quat_ve_lo_to_la_gi\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>L\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c phi\u00ean d\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1edfng. Trong l\u00f4 t\u00f4, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1ed3i ghi nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn tr\u00ean phi\u1ebfu v\u00e9 s\u1ed1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u00e9 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in s\u1eb5n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00fang th\u01b0\u1edfng trong <\/span><b>l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? N\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi phi\u00ean d\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ebft th\u00fac, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u00fang s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng v\u00e9 s\u1ed1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00fang. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa &amp; linh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho nh\u1eefng ai th\u00edch th\u1eed v\u1eadn may trong c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3364\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3364\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3364 size-full\" title=\"l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3364\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_dieu_kien_khi_tham_gia_vao_lo_to_la_gi\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n khi tham gia v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01a1i x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1eeb 18 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh vi d\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i hay l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ec9 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee7 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p &amp; an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3367\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3367\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3367 size-full\" title=\"l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n khi tham gia v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-1-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3367\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n khi tham gia v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tong_hop_thuat_ngu_quan_trong_khi_tham_gia_choi_lo_to\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quan tr\u1ecdng khi tham gia ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quan trong khi ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i SV368 g\u1ed3m c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lo_xien_So_da\"><\/span><b>L\u00f4 xi\u00ean\/ S\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00f4 xi\u00ean l\u00e0 khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi 2, 3 ho\u1eb7c 4 c\u1eb7p con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a 2 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 trong b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. C\u00e1c s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn trong kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 00 \u0111\u1ebfn 99. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd tr\u00fang gi\u1ea3i n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi trong k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bao_lo_Danh_lo\"><\/span><b>Bao l\u00f4\/ \u0110\u00e1nh l\u00f4<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bao l\u00f4 l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf mi\u1ec1n Trung, \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00f4 t\u00f4 2 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i trong ng\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t trong 18 gi\u1ea3i (mi\u1ec1n Trung &amp; mi\u1ec1n Nam) ho\u1eb7c 27 gi\u1ea3i (mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc).<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bach_thu_lo\"><\/span><b>B\u1ea1ch th\u1ee7 l\u00f4<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i tin l\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u00fang v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 trong ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m v\u1ed1n, ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Song_thu_lo\"><\/span><b>Song th\u1ee7 l\u00f4<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Song th\u1ee7 l\u00f4 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p s\u1ed1 trong l\u00f4 t\u00f4, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 trong c\u1eb7p l\u00f4 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ecdn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c, xem x\u00e9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u00fang th\u01b0\u1edfng khi tham gia v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3365\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3365\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3365 size-full\" title=\"l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quan tr\u1ecdng khi tham gia ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-3-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-3-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-3-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3365\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quan tr\u1ecdng khi tham gia ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_don_gian_de_choi_lo_to_la_gi\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m \u201cc\u00e1i\u201d: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ed1c ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 c\u1edd l\u00f4 t\u00f4 r\u1ed3i c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 d\u00f2 s\u1ed1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mua v\u00e9 l\u00f4 t\u00f4: M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea5m v\u00e9, tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 90, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o l\u00f4 t\u00f4 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f2 s\u1ed1: Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m \u201cc\u00e1i\u201d b\u1ed1c &amp; c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd d\u00f2 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o tr\u00f9ng kh\u1edbp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u ho\u1eb7c khoanh s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 5 con s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh theo h\u00e0ng ngang (ho\u1eb7c theo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc). Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd h\u00f4 to &#8220;kinh&#8221; \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3: Sau khi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f4 &#8220;kinh&#8221;, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m &#8220;c\u00e1i&#8221; s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang theo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &#8220;kinh&#8221; s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 sai s\u00f3t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &#8220;kinh&#8221; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u00e1p ph\u1ea1t t\u00f9y theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3366\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3366\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3366 size-full\" title=\"l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-2-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-2-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/lo-to-la-gi-2-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3366\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi tham gia v\u00e0o th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i <\/span><b>l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 h\u1eefu \u00edch h\u01a1n cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. <\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng SV368 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0 g\u00ec c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3 v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1. \u0110\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00eau trong b\u00e0i [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3368,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[7],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3363","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xo-so"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3363","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3363"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3363\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5857,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3363\/revisions\/5857"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3368"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3363"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3363"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3363"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}